---
title: "Tell me your situation"
description: "A few quick questions and I'll come back with a clear, honest plan — buying, selling, or figuring out your options."
crumbs: []
---
{#- CONTACT — intake form ported verbatim from production intake.html
    (sergeselenko/everlane-realty-site@main, fetched 2026-07-07).
    PREVIEW STATE: the endpoint string stays PRESERVED in /assets/site.js, but
    the form is rendered DISABLED — fields sit inside <fieldset disabled> and
    site.js carries a PREVIEW_MODE guard before any network path. Nothing can
    POST to the intake webhook from this build.
    Wave-1 addition lands below the form: Cal.com embedded booking (plan §2 #9).
    Radio group upgraded to fieldset/legend (audit §5.3). -#}

<div class="section">
  <div class="wrap form-wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">No pitch &mdash; a real plan</p>
    <h1 data-intake-title>Tell me your situation.</h1>
    <p class="lede" data-intake-lede>Give me the messy version &mdash; I&rsquo;ll make it clear. A few quick questions and I&rsquo;ll come back with an honest, comprehensive plan. Buying, selling, or just weighing your options.</p>

    <p class="form-disabled-note" role="note">Preview &mdash; form disabled</p>

    <div class="form-status" data-form-status role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>

    <form id="intake-form" novalidate>
      <fieldset class="form-preview-disabled" disabled>
        <div class="hp" aria-hidden="true">
          <label>Leave this field empty<input type="text" name="company" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off"></label>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="name">Your name <span class="hint">&mdash; so I know who I&rsquo;m helping</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" autocomplete="name" required>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid--2">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="phone">Cell <span class="hint">(optional)</span></label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="situation">What&rsquo;s the situation you&rsquo;d like a clear plan on?</label>
          <textarea id="situation" name="situation" placeholder="Tell me the messy version — I'll make it clear." required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <fieldset class="radio-fieldset">
            <legend>Is this mostly about&hellip;</legend>
            <div class="radio-row">
              <label><input type="radio" name="about" value="home" required> A home or property decision</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="about" value="business"> My business</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="about" value="other"> Something else</label>
            </div>
          </fieldset>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="outcome">What would a great outcome look like for you?</label>
          <textarea id="outcome" name="outcome" placeholder="The real goal, in your words."></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="context">Anything I should know? <span class="hint">&mdash; timeline, constraints, what you&rsquo;ve already tried</span></label>
          <textarea id="context" name="context" placeholder="Optional, but helpful."></textarea>
        </div>

        <input type="hidden" name="topic" value="" data-topic-field>
        <input type="hidden" name="source" value="intake-form">

        <p class="consent-note">By sending this, you&rsquo;re asking Serge Osaulenko (Everlane Realty) to follow up about your request. Your details are used only to prepare and discuss your plan &mdash; never sold or shared. You can ask to be removed anytime.</p>
        <p class="consent-note"><strong>Your privacy:</strong> the information you share here is stored securely, used only to respond to your request, never sold, rented, or shared with third parties, and deleted whenever you ask.</p>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--block" data-submit>Send it to Serge</button>
      </fieldset>
    </form>

    {%- if booking.calLink %}
    <div class="booking-inline" style="margin-top:32px">
      <p class="eyebrow">Or just grab a time</p>
      <h2>Book a consult directly</h2>
      <p class="lede">Pick a slot on Serge&rsquo;s live calendar &mdash; a free {{ booking.durationLabel }} call, no form first. Prefer to write? <a href="mailto:serge@everlanerealty.com">serge@everlanerealty.com</a> &middot; <a href="tel:+17274908037">727-490-8037</a>.</p>
      <div id="cal-inline" class="cal-embed" data-loading="Loading Serge&rsquo;s calendar&hellip;"></div>
      {% include "components/calcom-loader.njk" %}
      <script>Cal("inline", { elementOrSelector: "#cal-inline", calLink: "{{ booking.calLink }}", layout: "month_view" });</script>
    </div>
    {%- else %}
    <div class="stub-block" style="margin-top:32px">
      <strong>Book a consult directly</strong>
      <p style="margin:8px 0 0">The live Cal.com calendar embeds here once the booking link is set. Until then: <a href="mailto:serge@everlanerealty.com">serge@everlanerealty.com</a> &middot; <a href="tel:+17274908037">727-490-8037</a>.</p>
    </div>
    {%- endif %}
  </div>
</div>
